# Locked Google web login (AUTH-G1)

Canonical: [`.context/locked-auth-google.md`](../../.context/locked-auth-google.md) · [`docs/FIREBASE-AUTH-LATHUND.md`](../../docs/FIREBASE-AUTH-LATHUND.md)

## MUST

- `authDomain`: `gen-lang-client-0481875058.firebaseapp.com` (inte `web.app` utan GCP OAuth-URI)
- Prod web: `signInWithPopup` i vanlig flik; redirect endast `isStandalonePwa()`
- `VITE_GOOGLE_SIGNIN_REDIRECT` endast under `import.meta.env.DEV`
- `googleRedirectBoot` i `authRedirectBoot.ts` före React + PWA SW i `main.tsx`
- `prepareGoogleSignIn()` → `signOut` före Google på web
- Run `npm run smoke:auth-login` när du rör `src/modules/core/auth/*` eller `src/modules/core/firebase/init.ts`

## MUST NOT

- Tvinga alltid `signInWithRedirect` på desktop (regression 2026-06-12 / vit skärm)
- Prod-`authDomain` → `*.web.app` utan `redirect_uri` i GCP (fel 400)
- `VITE_GOOGLE_SIGNIN_REDIRECT=true` i Hosting CI secrets eller prod-build
- Ta bort `signInWithPopup` / `authRedirectBoot` utan produkt-OK + smoke PASS

Smoke: `npm run smoke:auth-login` (ingår i `smoke:locked-ux`)
